#: ../../../userspace-api/media/dvb/intro.rst:15
msgid ""
"The reader of this document is required to have some knowledge in the area "
"of digital video broadcasting (Digital TV) and should be familiar with part "
"I of the MPEG2 specification ISO/IEC 13818 (aka ITU-T H.222), i.e you should "
"know what a program/transport stream (PS/TS) is and what is meant by a "
"packetized elementary stream (PES) or an I-frame."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/dvb/intro.rst:21
msgid "Various Digital TV standards documents are available for download at:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/dvb/intro.rst:23
msgid ""
"European standards (DVB): http://www.dvb.org and/or http://www.etsi.org."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/dvb/intro.rst:24
msgid "American standards (ATSC): https://www.atsc.org/standards/"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/dvb/intro.rst:25
msgid "Japanese standards (ISDB): http://www.dibeg.org/"
msgstr ""

